OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,FWeight restrictions have been
OL,7,Fincreased on another London bridge
OL,8,Fbecause of safety concerns.
OL,10,FTransport for London (Tfl) announced a
OL,11,Fban on vehicles weighing more than 18
OL,12,Ftonnes from using Vauxhall Bridge in
OL,13,Fthe centre of the capital.
OL,15,FThis comes three months after Albert
OL,16,FBridge ` under two miles away ` was
OL,17,Fclosed to motor vehicles by Kensington
OL,18,Fand Chelsea Council after cracks were
OL,19,Ffound.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
