PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778771468
OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,FThe same restriction has also been
OL,7,Fimposed on Hammersmith Bridge, west
OL,8,FLondon, since April 2019 because of
OL,9,Fcracks in the pedestals.
OL,11,FTfL said its decision on Vauxhall
OL,12,FBridge was necessary because a recent
OL,13,Finspection found "some elements of the
OL,14,Fstructure have deteriorated".
OL,16,FBuses and emergency vehicles are
OL,17,Fexempt from the ban.
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
