OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,FTfL said Vauxhall Bridge carries an
OL,7,Faverage of 39,500 vehicles per day,
OL,8,Fabout 200 of which weigh more than 18
OL,9,Ftonnes.
OL,11,FThe bridge has been closed to abnormal
OL,12,Floads ` vehicles exceeding 44 tonnes
OL,13,For 11.5 tonnes per axle ` since 2023.
OL,15,FCarl Eddleston, TfL's director of
OL,16,Fstreets and network operations, said:
OL,17,F"Safety is our top priority, and we
OL,18,Fknow how important Vauxhall Bridge is
OL,19,Ffor people travelling across London.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778771468
OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,F"This is why we're taking this
OL,7,Fprecautionary step to introduce a
OL,8,Fweight restriction to the bridge.
OL,10,F"While the bridge remains safe,
OL,11,Flimiting heavier vehicles helps us
OL,12,Fprotect and keep it open while we
OL,13,Fdevelop the longterm improvements it
OL,14,Fneeds.
OL,16,F"We are sorry for any disruption
OL,17,Fcaused by the restriction, and we'll
OL,18,Fcontinue to monitor the area closely,
OL,19,Fensuring we keep people updated as
OL,20,Fthis work progresses."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
