CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778771468
OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,FSteve Gooding, director of motoring
OL,7,Fresearch charity the RAC Foundation,
OL,8,Ftold the Press Association: "We have
OL,9,Flong argued that the condition of road
OL,10,Fbridges serves as a lead indicator of
OL,11,Fthe highway maintenance problems that
OL,12,Fhave been building up as a result of
OL,13,Fageing structures, heavier traffic and
OL,14,Fenvironmental pressures.
OL,16,F"Commuters relying on the many bus
OL,17,Fservices that cross Vauxhall Bridge
OL,18,Feach day might be sighing with relief
OL,19,Fthat their journeys won't be affected
OL,20,Fby these restrictions.
OL,26,@pD@]OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
