OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778771468
OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,F"But at Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,7,Fheadquarters, barely half-a-mile away,
OL,8,Fthe question must be whether the new
OL,9,FStructures Fund will be anywhere near
OL,10,Flarge enough to address this growing
OL,11,Fchallenge seen not just in London but
OL,12,Fcountry-wide."
OL,14,FThe fund is available to councils in
OL,15,FEngland to repair their bridges,
OL,16,Fflyovers and tunnels.
OL,18,FIt is part of a #1 billion package to
OL,19,Ffix roads.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
