OL,3,CWeight restrictions imposed on another
OL,4,CLondon bridge
OL,6,FWhen the Government first announced
OL,7,Fthe scheme in June last year, it said
OL,8,Fabout 3,000 bridges across Britain
OL,9,Fwere unable to support the heaviest
OL,10,Fvehicles.
OL,12,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,13,Four political experts are across all
OL,14,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,15,Fto the latest episode below...
